message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and machine learning techniques for audio and speech processing. Other likely categories include cs.LG (machine learning), cs.CV (computer vision) as the proposed framework involves the use of CNNs and DNNs for feature extraction and classification. cs.CL (computational linguistics) and cs.MM (multimedia) are also possible categories as the proposed framework deals with audio classification tasks.
